# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible.
# turbo prune (inside the image) regenerates a pruned workspace from source,
# so we only need source + manifests + lockfile here — never build artifacts.

# Dependencies & build outputs
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage

# Rust desktop build output (gigabytes — must never enter the context)
apps/desktop/src-tauri/target

# Runtime data (local screenshots, etc.)
**/data

# Secrets — never bake env into images (compose provides env at runtime)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# VCS & misc
.git
.gitignore
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
.vscode
.idea
